name: INVISIBLE ALIENS
description:
Collage with over 150000 different aliens out of galaxies, from different times and worlds! 👽

I hope you can see them, all of them was captured on my 512-bit spectrum telescope with the E-Camera powered by Ethereum crystals, it was invented since I go to ethereum cave and found ethereum crystals, they have a huge amount of power, so I used them to build this E-Telescope. This is enough to look into different times and worlds, btw in the centre of our galaxy is nothing. There are no black holes. 🤷

This work u can be put on the wall into the frame.
The size of this collage is 10000x10000.
